data.enText: a name shared by all the members of a family (written last in English names)

simple_means.memory_skill: sur 上；超；外加 + name 名字 → 姓

tr: the name used to identify the members of a family (as distinguished from each member's given name)

value.def: Your surname is the name that you share with other members of your family. In English speaking countries and many other countries it is your last name.

example.tran: 她一直不知道他姓什么。

example.ex: The majority of British women adopt their husband's surname when they marry.
example.tran: 大多数英国女性结婚后随夫姓。
